name: Listened to Top takeaways from Miami’s 3-0 start

content.html:
Carlos Ledo of MIA All-Day Podcast joins Manny to discuss what we saw from Miami in its 48-7 win over Bethune-Cookman and what matters going forward. Plus, the two discuss the commitment of 2025 5-star DL Armondo Blount and answer mailbag questions. -Follow Manny on X/Twitter- @Manny_Navarro -Follow Carlos on X/Twitter- @ELLedo1307 Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
